    - need to make sure DC is a spearate RL pair, even when DC==0
  Debugging recodeBPic().

  The entire state diagram works, although there is still some parsing error.

10/16/98
  Two problems to fix:
    - syntax problem in ENTRY_B_PIC
      => problem is due to skipped MB in B picture.
      => need to change MB coding type if different QS is used.
    - temporal reference adjustment

  New B-picture skipped MB handling:
    if prediction direction is correct => remain coded as skipped MB.
    otherwise, recode (as Intra MB for the moment).

